
PHP index to organize a syllabus and highlight essential points:

Introduction to PHP: Basics, syntax, and installation.
Data Types and Variables: String, integer, arrays.
Control Structures: If, switch, loops.
Functions: Custom functions, parameters, return values.
Forms Handling: GET, POST methods.
Database Integration: MySQL connection, CRUD.
File Handling: Read, write, delete files.
Sessions & Cookies: User authentication.
Error Handling: Try-catch blocks, debugging.
Security Practices: SQL injection, XSS prevention.
